Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說啊 之前完全沒休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,和菲利斯聊工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯學姐也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才就看見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯也確認一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這回委託人是台場集群的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫維瓦爾第
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,台場 好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,台場怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,說到台場肯定是溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,集群各種溫泉都有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而且不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉是裸體天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐的真空機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,各位準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好了學姐 最終確認是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,每天沒裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐 這個人不會沒脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,台場集群禁止穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,台場集群禁止穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是頭一回沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 難道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對 畢竟有規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這種集群太匪夷所思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,給你看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,短褲沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只脫內褲就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊可以脫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是台場集群
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那個摩天輪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是帶浴池的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還有海灘的沙浴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那個富士山是圖像?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,投影在牆上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,還有畫舫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真有意境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺還挺舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,待久了感覺要生鏽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你說誰是廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐 先去泡會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,委託人還在等我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後再泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有時間一定去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,委託人不是神官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她住哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊的台場神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是神殿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,神官都要跑了 世界要完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼舒服的集群為什麼要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,各有各的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那是女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,女神？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是這個集群的仲裁者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人們會聚在雕像前的廣場做禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女神像也是真空的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人 內…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是異端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,頭待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你還穿著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,台場的各位都發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才不是說要脫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想脫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在馬上脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還有改過自新的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快從內褲族變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,脫掉 脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:35.54,Top,,0,0,0,,脫掉 脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我沒做錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個集群這就是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯現在快脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不脫才被追的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別拽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 放開我 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,掙扎會很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,誰想這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放手讓它來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那就該讓它脫下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以剛才不就那麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,總之快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和在大街上裸舞相當
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不妙 被發現只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就這還專家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想為了菲利斯學姐的內褲而死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯 現在也不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下內褲 舒適地工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我就替菲利斯保管內褲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好保管這內褲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,純潔正直的台場人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請回憶女神的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不應穿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,女神無論安寧還是波折
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都以身作則貫徹真空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,質疑女神者應遭天譴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,曾有人想偷窺女神像裙底確認真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,被成千的內褲染上了奇癢無比的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用說穿內褲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,必會受到更殘酷的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,維瓦爾第大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才又可疑人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿著內褲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要遭報應了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不必慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,女神在上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,邪道必將受到懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,神聖真空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,神聖真空 神聖真空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這只是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,請放心我們是偷渡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來幫您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我多麼盼望各位的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你手裡的不會是內褲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說出來很羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 在這集群裡就是異端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,自由 平等 真空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這是向台場女神發過的誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對於追求自由和風的人民而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,入浴後棄置的大量內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,會影響到生態圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在別的集群可以一直穿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,維瓦爾第女士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,偷渡後你現在的社會地位和財產都會化為烏有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,您願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,女神一定不會原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拋棄信仰同內褲遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼請在此畫押
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,身著禁止衣物的可疑人員目前在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,搜捕還在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因可疑人員持有手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,極度危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如有線索請到就近巡視員處檢舉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有風 走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,過分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來確認逃亡路線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們通過那個鍋爐到水上公車上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿爾加 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 大概是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,維瓦爾第女士 路線大概是這樣途經未知區域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,到達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要嚮導的話 我可以幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是穿過建築去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對 然後在水上公車站乘船離開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先去對面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,風有點大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我去還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別看 看下面 下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 為什麼讓我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 因為有可能敵人會埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 別往前看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會走光的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是這樣的地板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有別的路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是會走光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,終於出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好不容易撐到現在沒被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還能怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位快上船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,該船已掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微會有顛簸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯 進行火力壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在做 但是盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快用新宿時候的那什麼大招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這種情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,辦不了 都走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不就露個屁股至於嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 都是因為我想穿內褲的念頭造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,來導彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,絕活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,烏魯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿汪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐 又來了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,動手吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣準可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是陸地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩一發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,各位沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,總之還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,女神像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,奇癢無比的怪病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是天譴 天譴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼至今都沒注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,能看見字了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,寫的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,維瓦爾第大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,維瓦爾第大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這是女神的聖諭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,神回想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,過去有段穿內褲的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,民眾啊 穿上內褲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 只能一天一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲一天一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們踏出一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,女神赦免了內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,台場文明迎來了黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,烏魯拉還健在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 我好像不用逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我將繼續守護這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,守護內褲和真空的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 那不就白忙乎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞 她說放棄逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,仲裁者居然會變更集群的路線 聞所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你說赦免內褲一事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,對 一般是絕無可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們又偷摸幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在聊女神也會做出改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐請保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一直這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,回去還真空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞 把內褲還我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我一直好好保管著呢
